summary: it’s (almost) officially my second anniversary of watching dan and phil! (i’m a baby phannie) i remember when i watched my first...
body:
it’s (almost) officially my second anniversary of watching dan and phil! (i’m a baby phannie) i remember when i watched my first live show after messing about on youtube and i downloaded younow. i think it was his first ls of 2017, and i was at my grandmas on the floor with my phone plugged in. 2017 was a good year to join, tbh. i remember coming home after school and in my time zone, dan’s live shows would be right when i got off the bus and i’d watch them while i did dishes and cleaned & stuff. i think phils were during my school day and i usually watched them randomly ? also this was when u made my first ever video edits. they were imovie and they were awful but i was so happy.

anyways, big rant, but thank you dan and phil for giving me 2 years of happiness and enjoyment in the phandom
